/* Picture control that points to current attachment url ... */
Picture properties, XPath button, Show advanced view, Attachments, :attachmentURL

/* Picture control with preview functionality */
1. Select from Fields list, the field related to picture control.
2. Double-click and for default value, enter the following formula
   concat("http://XXXX:82/sites/trademarks/Lists/Trademarks/Attachments/"; ID; "/Logo.png")

